{"id":59,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":59,"title":"D&C 55","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 55"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to William W. Phelps, at Kirtland, Ohio, June 14, 1831. William W. Phelps, a printer, and his family had just arrived at Kirtland, and the Prophet sought the Lord for information concerning him."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.1-3"},"1–3"],", William W. Phelps is called and chosen to be baptized, to be ordained an elder, and to preach the gospel;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4"},"4"],", He is also to write books for children in Church schools;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.5-6"},"5–6"],", He is to travel to Missouri, which will be the area of his labors."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.1","order":"06.05.055.6711"},["b","1"],"Behold, thus saith the Lord unto you, my servant William, yea, even the Lord of the whole",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"earth"],", thou art called and chosen; and after thou hast been",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"baptized"],"by water, which if you do with an eye single to my glory, you shall have a remission of your sins and a reception of the Holy Spirit by the laying on of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"hands"],";"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.2","order":"06.05.055.6712"},["b","2"],"And then thou shalt be ordained by the hand of my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., to be an elder unto this church, to preach repentance and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"remission"],"of sins by way of baptism in the name of Jesus Christ, the Son of the living God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.3","order":"06.05.055.6713"},["b","3"],"And on whomsoever you shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"lay"],"your hands, if they are contrite before me, you shall have power to give the Holy Spirit."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4","order":"06.05.055.6714"},["b","4"],"And again, you shall be ordained to assist my servant Oliver Cowdery to do the work of printing, and of selecting and writing",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"books"],"for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"schools"],"in this church, that little",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"children"],"also may receive",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"instruction"],"before me as is pleasing unto me."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.5","order":"06.05.055.6715"},["b","5"],"And again, verily I say unto you, for this cause you shall take your journey with my servants Joseph Smith, Jun., and Sidney Rigdon, that you may be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"planted"],"in the land of your inheritance to do this work."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.6","order":"06.05.055.6716"},["b","6"],"And again, let my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Joseph Coe"],"also take his journey with them. The residue shall be made known hereafter, even as I will. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.1a","order":"06.05.055.6717"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/10.14"},"Deut. 10:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.6"},"1 Ne. 11:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.7"},"2 Ne. 29:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.1b","order":"06.05.055.6719"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-essential"},"TG Baptism, Essential"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.1c","order":"06.05.055.6721"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"TG Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.2a","order":"06.05.055.6723"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.3a","order":"06.05.055.6725"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.41"},"D&C 20:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4a","order":"06.05.055.6727"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.118"},"D&C 88:118"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.3.3-6"},"97:3 (3–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.7.7,14"},"109:7 (7, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4b","order":"06.05.055.6729"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/education"},"TG Education"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4c","order":"06.05.055.6731"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/children"},"TG Children"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.4d","order":"06.05.055.6733"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"},"TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.5a","order":"06.05.055.6735"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.15"},"Amos 9:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/55.6a","order":"06.05.055.6737"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/102.3.3,34"},"D&C 102:3 (3, 34)"],"."]]}
